item.title: Home
item.description: AI sensei is a multimedia platform that I created with a bunch of local data scientists. We aim to promote Data Science and AI in Hong Kong and other Asia countries. We release video every week on Youtube and write about AI every day on Facebook and Instagram. All videos are English subbed.
